This paper presents a new model for interpretable classification, which is a topic that falls under the machine learning and artificial intelligence fields. The paper also discusses the efficiency of feature utilization, which relates to data management and databases. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DM (Data Mining), cs.DB (Databases), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
